{"tid":641081,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"金球獎主辦單位向小白道歉","createTime":"2018-04-24T18:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T13:26:36.000Z","uid":54945,"like":17,"dislike":84,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"5599b1652cfb0489c55e3ae24bf9bb6c363e0ead","tid":641081,"uid":54945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T18:32:47.000Z","msg":"金球獎主辦單位向小白道歉<br />\n3小時前<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    小白很大機會在今季後離開母會巴塞隆拿。<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=jnl50lqomxNI%2F2fRpt5XFP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=3fd64c7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】金球獎的主辦單位法國雜誌《法國足球（France Football）》，在最新一期向恩尼斯達道歉，為甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n總編輯費利在最新一期的《法國足球》親自撰寫了一篇名為《請原諒我們，恩尼斯達》的文章，就雜誌從未把金球獎頒予對方而道歉。費利在文中讚揚恩尼斯達（Andres Iniesta）在足球生涯的豐功偉績：「恩尼斯達已證明了，當談及冠軍時，腦袋絕對是最重要的事。」<br />\n<br />\n在美斯及基斯坦奴朗拿度壟斷金球獎的情況下，小白接近的1次是2010年，就算於世界盃決賽射入奠勝球，助西班牙國家隊登頂，仍然只能獲得第2名；至於2012年，他助狂牛兵團衛冕歐國盃，則成為第3名。<br />\n<br />\n33歲的小白很大機會在今季後離開母會巴塞隆拿，盛傳在短時間內就會公佈轉戰中超，不過有指阿仙奴及曼城都極力邀請這名中場魔術師加盟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牙朗是咪要扣番一個金球掌<br />\n姐係而家得4個<br />\n少美斯1個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd70734510bfac0fcdfdf25615ff3d85088f4ed5","tid":641081,"uid":37735,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T18:34:56.000Z","msg":"一個佢 一個史奈達"},{"pid":"9cede77fe478f62e6bdd307f13d8b01daafaf75f","tid":641081,"uid":133546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T18:35:57.000Z","msg":"雙金球<br />\n打和 super！"},{"pid":"a2963841ed5184139f0e16132d5cce8bbe463363","tid":641081,"uid":65342,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"cd70734510bfac0fcdfdf25615ff3d85088f4ed5","tid":641081,"uid":37735,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T18:34:56.000Z","msg":"一個佢 一個史奈達"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T18:36:08.000Z","msg":"仲有個列貝利"},{"pid":"e10891b04016689419b7f8bc95c254017a9c6465","tid":641081,"uid":1291,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T18:36:51.000Z","msg":"仲有我個金裘掌"},{"pid":"7926592a2f0aaaa66525e6bae04aeb611a42c941","tid":641081,"uid":137605,"like":125,"dislike":0,"score":125,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T18:39:11.000Z","msg":"2010 2012 全部美斯拎喎 扣牙朗一個?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562194e2ae014be20b198e68d0837ee82a5322bb","tid":641081,"uid":54000,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T18:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/25/024007_6057a350876b41bf162bdbe72df6277a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2F024007_6057a350876b41bf162bdbe72df6277a.png&h=43ca972c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ca3aa2d1fbd312e96a728ae540f00e9f97c5835","tid":641081,"uid":54000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"562194e2ae014be20b198e68d0837ee82a5322bb","tid":641081,"uid":54000,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T18:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/25/024007_6057a350876b41bf162bdbe72df6277a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2F024007_6057a350876b41bf162bdbe72df6277a.png&h=43ca972c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T18:40:24.000Z","msg":"自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23808b19cd463750b27efaf318bdf87df9b215e","tid":641081,"uid":1291,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"562194e2ae014be20b198e68d0837ee82a5322bb","tid":641081,"uid":54000,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T18:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/2